sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant AG as autogluonserver<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as kserve-storage<br/>(in-process)
    participant Cloud as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>/mnt/models

    Note over AG,Cloud: Flow 2: Model Loading at Startup

    AG->>AG: ensure_autogluon_runtime_paths()<br/>Set writable CWD for OpenShift
    AG->>Storage: Storage.download(storageUri)
    Storage->>Cloud: GET model artifacts<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials (IAM/SA/Token)
    Cloud-->>Storage: Model files
    Storage->>FS: Write to /mnt/models
    AG->>AG: PredictorFactory.detect()<br/>Try TimeSeriesPredictor first
    alt TimeSeriesPredictor detected
        AG->>AG: TimeSeriesPredictor.load(/mnt/models)
    else TabularPredictor fallback
        AG->>AG: TabularPredictor.load(/mnt/models)
    end
    AG->>AG: ModelServer.start()<br/>Listen 8080/TCP HTTP + 8081/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,AG: Flow 1: Tabular Inference (v1)

    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Ingress->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    RBAC->>RBAC: Validate token
    RBAC->>AG: Forward 8080/TCP HTTP<br/>(localhost, no auth)
    AG->>AG: Parse JSON → pandas DataFrame
    AG->>AG: TabularPredictor.predict(df)
    AG-->>RBAC: JSON prediction result
    RBAC-->>Ingress: Response
    Ingress-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,AG: Flow 1b: Tabular Inference (v2)

    Client->>Ingress: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Ingress->>RBAC: Forward request
    RBAC->>AG: Forward 8080/TCP HTTP
    AG->>AG: InferRequest tensors → DataFrame<br/>Map tensor names to columns
    AG->>AG: TabularPredictor.predict(df)
    AG-->>RBAC: InferResponse tensors
    RBAC-->>Ingress: Response
    Ingress-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,AG: Flow 3: Time Series Inference (v1 only)

    Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Ingress->>RBAC: Forward request
    RBAC->>AG: Forward 8080/TCP HTTP
    AG->>AG: Parse JSON → TimeSeriesDataFrame
    AG->>AG: TimeSeriesPredictor.predict(tsdf)
    AG-->>RBAC: JSON prediction result
    RBAC-->>Ingress: Response
    Ingress-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,AG: Metrics Scraping

    Ingress->>AG: GET /metrics (8080/TCP)
    AG-->>Ingress: Prometheus metrics
